quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  5,20,Recall ut Moses dictus to his people O my people remember deus blessings vos He appointed prophets vos factus vos rex granted vos quod He nunquam granted any alius people
  5,21,O my people iniit sanctus terra ut DEUS decretum vos non rebel lest vos become losers
  5,22,They dictus O Moses ibi est powerful people it nos non iniit it they get it they get nos iniit
  5,23,vir reverent beatus DEUS dictus Just iniit gate Vos just iniit it vos surely prevail Vos trust DEUS vos est believers
  5,24,They dictus O Moses nos nunquam iniit it long prout they est it Ergo iit! - Vos tuus Dominus - Ac fight Nos sitting rectus hic
  5,25,He dictus My Dominus ego unus control my frater. Ita allow nos part company wicked people
  5,26,He dictus Henceforth it forbidden them 40 annus quae they roam terra aimlessly. Non grieve such wicked people